    "description": "<strong>IMMERSE YOURSELF IN THE WORLD OF SHOOTING SPORTS!</strong><br>Welcome to #tacticalunderground arcade, a hardcore shooter with a top view. All matches are randomly generated, so it is important to familiarize yourself with the briefing before starting the passage. Use left/right tilts to hit targets from behind corners, thanks to the advanced character control mechanics.<br>In the game you will have to go through 3 seasons of the shooting tournament series #tacticalunderground. These tournaments were previously held in the real world!<br><br><strong>GO THROUGH THE EXERCISES AT MAXIMUM SPEED</strong><br>The most important thing for you is time and the availability of ammunition! There are no indicators and counters, everything is like in the real world, where you will know the result only after the end of the match.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211030/extras/c5b947bb5c3d8dbcd3ea30a66dae062f.poster.avif?t=1724864779\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211030/extras/c5b947bb5c3d8dbcd3ea30a66dae062f.webm?t=1724864779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211030/extras/c5b947bb5c3d8dbcd3ea30a66dae062f.mp4?t=1724864779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>SURVIVE AND BREAK THROUGH</strong><br>The game features arcade modes &quot;Breakthrough&quot; and &quot;Survival&quot;, where you will need to fight off &quot;virtual&quot; targets. Your goal is to avoid the approach of targets, as well as to stay in place or reach a safe place.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211030/extras/53a9871b01000084ea2f93f4b2c1a560.poster.avif?t=1724864779\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211030/extras/53a9871b01000084ea2f93f4b2c1a560.webm?t=1724864779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211030/extras/53a9871b01000084ea2f93f4b2c1a560.mp4?t=1724864779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>PLAY WITH FRIENDS</strong><br>Go through cooperative matches, or fight in competitive modes.<br>Play locally or online thanks to the support of the Steam - Remote Play Together feature!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211030/extras/63d30ac4b1aacd57901957c9c79b8fa8.poster.avif?t=1724864779\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211030/extras/63d30ac4b1aacd57901957c9c79b8fa8.webm?t=1724864779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211030/extras/63d30ac4b1aacd57901957c9c79b8fa8.mp4?t=1724864779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
